data.description: NOW OFFERING A 2.5% CLOSING COST CREDIT WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER! Use these funds towards your closing costs or enjoy a 3-2-1 RATE BUY DOWN!! This credit will allow you to marry the house and date the rate! Sellers are motivated and ready to move on to their next stage! This beautiful home shows like a model!  Meticulously maintained MAIN LEVEL LIVING in the heart of Nokesville! Enjoy one level living on an easy to maintain 1 acre lot while remaining in close proximity to the major employment corridors of the DMV.  Built in 2020, this home is better than new!  Featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms and over 3600 sq ft of finished living space, you will not want to let this one get away!  You will love the open, free flowing floor plan that allows for endless entertaining opportunities. You are greeted by a very welcoming front porch, spanning the length of the home, allowing ample space for multiple rocking chairs to enjoy the cool Virginia evenings. Upon entry to the home, the foyer opens to the heart of the home, boasting high ceilings throughout, immaculate luxury vinyl plank flooring and a wide-open floor plan. This home was designed for easy living, featuring a split bedroom floor plan with an enormous gourmet kitchen, breakfast room and spacious living room in between. The kitchen will please the most discerning chef, with gas cooking, 42” cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a large walk-in pantry and oversized island opening to the breakfast room.  The breakfast area leads to the Trex deck and screened in porch via french door access . The kitchen opens to the living room as well, allowing a fantastic entertaining flow throughout the main level. The primary suite is a delight! Boasting a gorgeous tray ceiling, abundant natural light, immaculate luxury vinyl plank flooring, two walk in closets and a spa like primary bath! The primary suite is tucked away on the left side of the home, allowing both privacy and easy access to the 2 main level junior bedrooms. The 2 main level junior bedrooms both feature ample closet space, abundant natural light and easy access to the shared hall bathroom. The main level is further completed by a formal dining room, currently being used as a home office, laundry room, and a very functional mud room off the garage entrance. On the upper level, find the 4th bedroom, a fantastic loft area that is the perfect hangout for the kids and another full bathroom. The lower level has been partially finished, boasting a very large recreation room that is a great space for big game night or the family to gather! There is an oversized unfinished area with rough in plumbing waiting for your finishing touches as well as an additional unfinished area being used for storage. The back yard is likely where you will want to spend your free time! Enjoy a screened in porch with ceiling fan, Trex deck and stairs leading down to the backyard firepit and stone patio. The large flat lot is perfect for a play set, a family football game or maybe a pool? At the rear of the lot, find a shed with ramp for all of your outdoor toys. The two car front load garage has been freshly painted and the floor covered in epoxy. Highly desired BDHS and TNS.
